{"tid":437122,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇係外國讀過書嘅巴絲同我一樣","createTime":"2017-10-15T16:48:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-16T12:57:47.000Z","uid":35606,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ddbed3025fdfd0443592cdda518f420b4051c0d7","tid":437122,"uid":35606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T16:48:49.000Z","msg":"岩岩去左兩個幾月，係外國其實好悶。<br />\n唔似讀bachelor 咁可以識好多人。讀master同學唔多，好多都係原校bachelor 上master，有晒自己圈子，一係就好難約，因為住係第個city。<br />\n言語不通，睇會大概明意思，識講少少，但聽仲差好遠，淨係係大學入面先講到英文，但大學以外範圍基本上同聾左冇分別。<br />\n除左返學之外基本上好懶出街，除左好多書要溫之外，就係因為岩岩講嗰啲唔太想面對人，但係我本身係一個好out going嘅人，所我真係唔想咁毒，淨係掛住讀書。<br />\n有冇巴絲一樣？你地點樣克服呢種心態<br />\n<br />\n利申：歐洲非英語國家"},{"pid":"1625e93d9d024b31ecc6fb868af72909b4243379","tid":437122,"uid":35606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T16:52:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28511bc03fa2a497b8bc092ff4abe7b37e2adfd6","tid":437122,"uid":38746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T17:45:32.000Z","msg":"我join好多soc 幾好玩wo"},{"pid":"407945b90371827c811baa3617898a02e3972152","tid":437122,"uid":85444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T18:27:47.000Z","msg":"當地冇華人? 應該唔多唔少都會有d <br />\n試下搵下 得閒出黎食餐飯 人都會開心d"},{"pid":"5afa6553a5b6d4cc095c0390372a04a2a75eefc3","tid":437122,"uid":131926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T05:27:02.000Z","msg":"唔好比理由自己 走出Comfort zone"},{"pid":"91d4933f80d634c37a366740e6c29ccd5c3eb707","tid":437122,"uid":76245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T05:37:11.000Z","msg":"讀學士/master/phd都係一樣，<br />\n去到外國想學校識朋友要主動d，<br />\n怕怕羞羞咁真係永遠無乜朋友"},{"pid":"f0db4d481c51c7d664050bc17c27622328b47100","tid":437122,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T05:39:53.000Z","msg":"巴打係邊到讀啊"},{"pid":"695feeb7b886825d1f49cac4004812cf7e1caacc","tid":437122,"uid":12980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T05:48:43.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過係你唔肯埋當地人堆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddcc7b0ac5c05cf05a125909251f174e0f32918b","tid":437122,"uid":12980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T05:50:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好比理由自己 走出Comfort zone</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你行出去 主動聊人講野<br />\n有返啲自信 大家都係後生仔<br />\n厚面皮啲好快就會識到新朋友"},{"pid":"d1efd2049acc2907a007f74ba4dd3561cf8790fe","tid":437122,"uid":35606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T11:41:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當地冇華人? 應該唔多唔少都會有d <br />\n試下搵下 得閒出黎食餐飯 人都會開心d</blockquote><br />\n有係有，不過真係少，我faculty 我一個華人，又唔見到其他faculty 嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e65fe27690478b45f32a33204da8055b1219d33","tid":437122,"uid":35606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T12:53:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔好比理由自己 走出Comfort zone</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你行出去 主動聊人講野<br />\n有返啲自信 大家都係後生仔<br />\n厚面皮啲好快就會識到新朋友</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你地都岩嘅，我都明過渡期一定會咁，但係有時溝通真心覺得攰，<br />\n我成日都試用佢地嘅語言去問野或者傾計，但係佢地知我講得唔好會用返英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後有啲英文唔好嘅人就要一路查字典一路同我講，都幾攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2476f6020d30d751d5a0242cf0d2b76620ab4f6c","tid":437122,"uid":35606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T12:57:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打係邊到讀啊</blockquote><br />\n葡萄牙"}]}